<h1 id="codemismatch-theme">CodeMismatch Theme</h1>

<p>Enterprise AI consultancy theme with dynamic theming, color customization, and interactive features.</p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>ğŸ¨ <strong>3 Theme Modes</strong>: Void (Dark), Azure (Light Gradient), Paper (Clean Light)</li>
  <li>ğŸŒˆ <strong>Dynamic Color Palettes</strong>: Real-time brand and ambient color customization</li>
  <li>ğŸŒŠ <strong>Animated Canvas Background</strong>: Smooth wave animations</li>
  <li>ğŸ’¬ <strong>AI Chat Interface</strong>: â€œThe Architectâ€ chat UI (requires Gemini API)</li>
  <li>ğŸ“± <strong>Fully Responsive</strong>: Mobile-first design with touch-friendly controls</li>
  <li>ğŸ”— <strong>Browser History Support</strong>: Back/forward navigation with URL hashes</li>
  <li>âš¡ <strong>Optimized</strong>: 377 lines of clean JavaScript, 12KB total</li>
</ul>

